# Extract Pages from PDF

# Description

Extracts a new PDF document from the specified page range of an existing PDF.

# Project compatibility

Windows | Cross-platform

# Configuration

* 
* Start range - Enter the page number you want to extract from. This field supports Double type input.
* End range - Enter the page number you want to extract until. This field supports Double type input.
* File - The file to use. This field supports IResource type input.









* Split PDF - The split PDF. Automatically generated output variable.
* Document ID - The unique identifier for the PDF document.
